column2: SELECT s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zWarning, s.class, s.subClass, s.sciencePrimary,   s.survey, s.programname, s.legacy_target1, s.boss_target1,   s.bestObjID FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN specObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID = p.objID JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID = p.objID WHERE s.ra BETWEEN # and #  AND s.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND s.class = &&&  AND (legacy_target1 & (# | # | #)) > #  AND s.z BETWEEN # and #  AND s.zWarning = # ORDER BY s.z
